295
00:13:10,530 --> 00:13:11,690
She's cute.

296
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:13,460
She's just a friend.

297
00:13:13,530 --> 00:13:17,370
R-R-R-uff.

298
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,480
